metadata.name: Expanding energy
metadata.description:
Calligraphic brush strokes expressing movement of energy and information.  
May this piece expand the positive energies to you. You can also share the good energies, you can mint how many editions you want and airdrop it for your loved ones.  
Much love, Jackson Alves.
